# 🚀 DEPLOYMENT SCRIPTS FOR PRODUCTION

## Backend Deployment
```bash
# Navigate to backend directory
cd c:\Users\Jakgrits\project-mgnt\backend

# Install dependencies
npm ci

# Build for production
npm run build

# Start production server
npm start
```

## Frontend Deployment
```bash
# Navigate to frontend directory
cd c:\Users\Jakgrits\project-mgnt\next-app

# Install dependencies
npm ci

# Build for production
npm run build

# Start production server
npm start
```

